[207.248719, "o", "\r\n  Based on Sprint 1 retro, the PO Agent will receive:\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mImprovements to apply:\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[33m1.\u001b[0m Add departure deadline constraint\r\n       \u001b[2mTruck must depart by hour X — window must end before deadline\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[33m2.\u001b[0m Multi-truck fleet scheduling\r\n       \u001b[2mN chargers shared by M trucks — capacity constraints\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[33m3.\u001b[0m Input validation for CSV loader\r\n       \u001b[2mReviewer flagged: hour bounds, missing data warnings\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[33m4.\u001b[0m CLI interface for fleet operators\r\n       \u001b[2margparse: --csv prices.csv --trucks 5 --chargers 3\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[2mTo run Sprint 2:\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2m$ python3 orchestrator.py \"Improve the charging optimizer: add departure\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2m  deadline, multi-truck scheduling, input validation, and CLI\"\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
